query ($query:[QueryStatementInput])
{
	bplusItSappiGetContacts (query: $query)
	{
		id
		tenantId
		tenantCode
		systemId
		systemName
		roleId
		roleName
		name
		surname
		email
		mobile
		area
		hasConsentEmail
		hasConsentMobile
		isActive
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

query ($query:[QueryStatementInput])
{
	bplusItSappiFindContact (query: $query)
	{
		id
		tenantId
		tenantCode
		systemId
		systemName
		roleId
		roleName
		name
		surname
		email
		mobile
		area
		hasConsentEmail
		hasConsentMobile
		isActive
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

query ($id:ID)
{

		tenantCode

		roleName
		name
		surname
		email
		mobile

		updatedAt
	}
}
